<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Parcel Delivered - FMS</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header-title {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .success-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .delivery-confirmation {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fff8;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #28a745;
        }

        .confirmation-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .parcel-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .tracking-image {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 20px auto;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .notice-box {
            background-color: #e8f4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #1e3c72;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #1e3c72;
        }
        
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #1e3c72;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .timestamp {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                width: 100% !important;
            }
            
            .email-body {
                padding: 20px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1 class="header-title">Delivery Confirmation</h1>
            <div class="success-badge">✓ Delivered</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <div class="delivery-confirmation">
                <div class="confirmation-icon">✓</div>
                <h2>Package Successfully Delivered!</h2>
                <p>Your shipment has reached its destination</p>
            </div>

            <p>Dear <%= sendername %>,</p>
            <p>We're pleased to inform you that your parcel has been successfully delivered. Here are the delivery details:</p>
            
            <div class="parcel-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">From:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= from %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">To:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= to %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Sender:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= sendername %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Recipient:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= recipientname %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Cost:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">$<%= cost %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Weight:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= weight %> g</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row" style="border-bottom: none;">
                    <span class="detail-label">Note:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= note %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <img class="tracking-image" 
                 src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1717495157/hero_r5lgvq.png" 
                 alt="Delivery Confirmation">
            
            <div class="notice-box">
                <strong>Delivery Note:</strong><br>
                If you have any concerns about this delivery or weren't expecting this package, 
                please contact our support team immediately.
            </div>

            <div class="timestamp">
                Delivered on: <%= new Date().toISOString().replace('T', ' ').slice(0, 19) %> UTC
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <strong>Need assistance?</strong><br>
                Contact our support team:<br>
                Email: <a href="mailto:support@fms-system.com">support@fms-system.com</a><br>
                Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Track Another Parcel</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">View Delivery History</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
                © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> FMS - Freight Management System. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>